{"id":561639,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/06/公民博客｜抓捕胡锡进，刻不容缓！/","date":"2017-06-20T00:46:19Z","modified":"2017-06-20T00:46:19Z","title":"公民博客｜抓捕胡锡进，刻不容缓！","content":"<p><strong>中国数字时代编辑注：经查证，该文已被删除，网页显示：“此内容因违规无法查看。由用户投诉并经平台审核，涉嫌违反相关法律法规和政策。”</strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #010101\">很明显，我的上一篇奏章</span><a href=\"http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI0MjE4MDQ2MA==&amp;mid=2247484004&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=f1f811cae2283d0111ea6b748e87ce3d&amp;chksm=e9010a67de768371de9c5cb178681d2655a1454cb992e8f476b05416be4bc42a05137bb5e95b&amp;scene=21 \\l wechat_redirect\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff\"><u>《环球时报，不火上浇油能死吗？》</u></span></a><span style=\"color: #010101\">，完全没有引起有关部门的重视，更不可能上达圣听。言犹在耳，这头披着人皮的白眼儿狼，已经跳起了失心舞，扬起了招魂幡，与郭大观一唱一和，春风得意马蹄疾，愿作鸳鸯不羡仙。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #010101\">看看白眼儿狼的新题目，《因负罪而恐惧的郭盘古用谎言壮胆》。套路还是一样的套路，但是猖狂加倍有恃无恐，闲庭信步一般报道郭大观的最新动态。终其全篇，</span><span style=\"color: #010101;font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">“</span><span style=\"color: #010101\">谎言</span><span style=\"color: #010101;font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">”</span><span style=\"color: #010101\">长</span><span style=\"color: #010101;font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">“</span><span style=\"color: #010101\">谎言</span><span style=\"color: #010101;font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">”</span><span style=\"color: #010101\">短，除了</span><span style=\"color: #010101;font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">“</span><span style=\"color: #010101\">爆料</span><span style=\"color: #010101;font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">”</span><span style=\"color: #010101\">，除了</span><span style=\"color: #010101;font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">“</span><span style=\"color: #010101\">政治诽谤</span><span style=\"color: #010101;font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">”</span><span style=\"color: #010101\">，又引入了</span><span style=\"color: #010101;font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">“</span><span style=\"color: #010101\">离奇故事</span><span style=\"color: #010101;font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">”</span><span style=\"color: #010101\">，没有相当的政治觉悟，好奇心严重的群众即便躲过了上一次的暗箭，又怎么经得住这一回的明枪？</span></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_283567\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img class=\"wp-image-283567 size-full\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/胡锡进.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/胡锡进.jpg 500w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/03/胡锡进-300x199.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">胡锡进。图片来自网络</p></div>\n<p><span style=\"color: #010101;font-family: 'Times New Roman'\"></p>\n<p></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #010101\">胡锡进是有点儿失心疯了，甚至给群众寻找郭大观配备了谷歌地图：</span><span style=\"color: #010101;font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">“</span><span style=\"color: #010101\">郭大观主要剩下在社交媒体上发文字帖和视频了。</span><span style=\"color: #010101;font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">”</span><span style=\"color: #010101\">如此大张旗鼓在境内给郭大观招兵买马，是还嫌他的</span><span style=\"color: #010101;font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">“</span><span style=\"color: #010101\">推友</span><span style=\"color: #010101;font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">”</span><span style=\"color: #010101\">数量不够多、</span><span style=\"color: #010101;font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">YouTube</span><span style=\"color: #010101\">粉丝不够疯吗？</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #010101\">白眼儿狼显然意犹未尽，依旧假装疯魔以退为进：</span><span style=\"color: #010101;font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">“</span><span style=\"color: #010101\">不能不说，他仍是一个热闹，境内外一些对中国政治制度怀恨在心的人，以及就是喜欢政治谣言刺激的人，有些仍愿意凑他这个热闹。</span><span style=\"color: #010101;font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">”</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #010101\">没有你胡内奸开门揖盗，除了伦敦大火巴拿马反水，善良的人们去哪里知道还有这种</span><span style=\"color: #010101;font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">“</span><span style=\"color: #010101\">热闹</span><span style=\"color: #010101;font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">”</span><span style=\"color: #010101\">？胡锡进，你欲擒故纵的小伎俩，已经炉火纯青了。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #010101;font-family: 'Times New Roman'\"></p>\n<p></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #010101\">还有更露骨的诱饵。</span><span style=\"color: #010101;font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">“</span><span style=\"color: #010101\">据说郭大观给自己搞了一个庞大的顾问团和律师团，还听说他现在有三十几名保镖</span><span style=\"color: #010101;font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">”</span><span style=\"color: #010101\">，</span><span style=\"color: #010101;font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">“</span><span style=\"color: #010101\">尤其令人惊讶的是，他竟然在美国动员华人争取搞一个</span><span style=\"color: #010101;font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">‘</span><span style=\"color: #010101\">感美日</span><span style=\"color: #010101;font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">’</span><span style=\"color: #010101\">，感谢美国带给大家的</span><span style=\"color: #010101;font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">‘</span><span style=\"color: #010101\">庇护</span><span style=\"color: #010101;font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">’</span><span style=\"color: #010101\">和</span><span style=\"color: #010101;font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">‘</span><span style=\"color: #010101\">安全</span><span style=\"color: #010101;font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">’</span><span style=\"color: #010101\">。</span><span style=\"color: #010101;font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">”</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #010101;font-family: 'Times New Roman'\"></p>\n<p></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #010101\">这是干什么？这不就是在洋洋得意地详解什么是</span><span style=\"color: #010101;font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">“</span><span style=\"color: #010101\">热闹</span><span style=\"color: #010101;font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">”</span><span style=\"color: #010101\">好让群众窥一斑想全豹吗？哼哼，山高月小，水落石出，任你一会儿雾霾一会儿云烟乔装改扮仿佛为国分忧的司马南，我自兵来将挡水来土掩火眼金睛认得你是里通外国的狗汉奸！</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #010101;font-family: 'Times New Roman'\"></p>\n<p></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #010101\">他郭盘古在前，你胡锡进在后，他郭大观冲锋陷阵，你胡锡进捷报频传。但看这对青年才俊，一个擎着鹦鹉，一个架着老鸦。一个向壁虚构离家万里搬砖弄瓦，一个吃里扒外近在咫尺蹿上跳下。一个是一阵黄风一阵沙，一个学金莲假寐葡萄架。一个是语不惊人死不休，一个装神弄鬼暗度陈仓全当圣上是睁眼瞎。</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #010101\">抓捕胡锡进，刻不容缓！</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #010101\">这些年看了些荣枯，也经了些成败，知道蚁穴能溃千里堤，小恶不除贻大害。先贤在光辉著作《左传》里早已经说过：胡氏何厌之有？不如早为之所，无使滋蔓，蔓，难图也。蔓草犹不可除，况君之宠臣乎？</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #010101\">抓捕胡锡进，刻不容缓！</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #010101\">现在，胡锡进的狐狸尾巴还在遮遮掩掩，说明他还没有那么大的把握吹响号角冲下山，说明他还在打着相机而动的小算盘。对待这种狼心狗肺的卖国贼，一忍再忍是心存怜悯，三忍四忍就是脑子有病。我们真要等到他把</span><span style=\"color: #010101;font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">“</span><span style=\"color: #010101\">社交媒体上的文字和视频</span><span style=\"color: #010101;font-family: 'Times New Roman'\">”</span><span style=\"color: #010101\">原封不动地引进来那天才能恍然大悟吗？</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #010101\">亡羊补牢未为晚，此时不将狗贼麻利拿下，千年大计，真有可能毁于一旦！</span></p>\n","author":1052,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,17016,9203],"tags":[32879,14004,15525]}